org.gvsig.scripting

Interface ScriptingHelpManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultScriptingHelpManager

    public interface ScriptingHelpManager
    This class is responsable of the management of the Help services provided to the application. It shows all the methods applied to the JavaDocs imported on the ScriptingFramework
    See Also:
    ScriptingManager
